casebody.data:
No. 09-728. Jon A. Jensen, et ux., Petitioners v. Paul A. Stoot, Sr., et al. 559 U.S. 1057, 130 S. Ct. 2343, 2010 U.S. LEXIS 3013.

176 L. Ed. 2d 577,

April 5, 2010.

Motion of National Association of Police Organizations, Inc. for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Motion of City of Escondido for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.

Same case below, 582 F.3d 910.
